#. type: Plain text
#: _posts/2021-03-04-path-resolution-in-quarkus.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"Once upon a time, Quarkus defined additional endpoints for things like "
"health checks and metrics. They were served from the `quarkus.http.root-"
"path` alongside any endpoints the application defined. This isn't always "
"obvious, as `quarkus.http.root-path` is `/` by default, making it "
"effectively invisible."
msgstr ""
"很久以前，Quarkus为健康检查和指标等事项定义了额外的端点。它们从 `quarkus.http.root-path` "
"，与应用程序定义的任何端点一起提供服务。这并不总是很明显，因为 `quarkus.http.root-path` 默认为 `/` "
"，这使得它实际上是看不见的。"

#. type: Plain text
#: _posts/2021-03-04-path-resolution-in-quarkus.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"As these proliferated, we started worrying about link:https://groups.google."
"com/g/quarkus-dev/c/FMnmlDIcGRY[polluting the application endpoint "
"namespace], and thinking about how we could group these non-application "
"endpoints together to avoid colliding with application endpoints and make it "
"easier to deal with security and access policies. Some users further asked "
"if we could serve these non-application endpoints from link:https://github."
"com/quarkusio/quarkus/issues/13602[another port entirely] (we haven't gotten "
"there yet)."
msgstr ""
"随着这些终端的激增，我们开始担心会 link:https://groups.google.com/g/quarkus-dev/c/"
"FMnmlDIcGRY[污染应用终端的命名空间] "
"，并考虑如何将这些非应用终端分组，以避免与应用终端发生冲突，并使安全和访问策略更容易处理。一些用户进一步询问我们是否可以 link:https://"
"github.com/quarkusio/quarkus/issues/13602[完全] 从 link:https://github.com/"
"quarkusio/quarkus/issues/13602[另一个端口] 为这些非应用端点提供服务（我们还没有达到这个目的）。"

#. type: Plain text
#: _posts/2021-03-04-path-resolution-in-quarkus.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"The first step was to group all of these extension-defined endpoints "
"together. This was the genesis of the link:https://github.com/quarkusio/"
"quarkus/pull/13601[non-application endpoint path]. The default location of "
"this new path was `/q`, and it was nested under the HTTP root path, just as "
"the other endpoints had been. The effect was to move `/health` to `/q/"
"health`, as an example."
msgstr ""
"第一步是将所有这些扩展定义的端点组合在一起。这 link:https://github.com/quarkusio/quarkus/pull/"
"13601[就是非应用端点路径] 的起源。这个新路径的默认位置是 `/q` ，它被嵌套在HTTP根路径下，就像其他端点一样。其效果是将 `/"
"health` 移到 `/q/health` ，作为一个例子。"

#. type: Plain text
#: _posts/2021-03-04-path-resolution-in-quarkus.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"We knew that moving some of these endpoints, like metrics and health, would "
"be problematic for already deployed applications and human muscle memory. To "
"ease the transition, we added redirects for some of these endpoints, so that "
"if you visited `/metrics` you would be redirected to `/q/metrics`."
msgstr ""
"我们知道，移动其中的一些端点，如指标和健康状况，对于已经部署的应用程序和人类的肌肉记忆来说，会有问题。为了缓解过渡，我们为其中一些端点添加了重定向，这样，如果你访问了 "
"`/metrics` ，就会被重定向到 `/q/metrics` 。"

#. type: Plain text
#: _posts/2021-03-04-path-resolution-in-quarkus.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "Non-application endpoint support shipped in `1.11.0.Final`."
msgstr "非应用端点支持在 `1.11.0.Final` 。"

#. type: Plain text
#: _posts/2021-03-04-path-resolution-in-quarkus.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"And then things started to link:https://github.com/quarkusio/quarkus/pull/"
"14179[go] link:https://github.com/quarkusio/quarkus/issues/15030[sideways]. "
"Some cloud hosting providers only accept `200` as a definition of health, "
"for example, so the redirect (a `301`) didn't have the intended effect. "
"There was also some confusion about how to turn the non-application endpoint "
"off to return to previous behavior, and further questions about how to move "
"specific endpoints out of this non-application endpoint collection."
msgstr ""
"然后事情就开始 link:https://github.com/quarkusio/quarkus/pull/14179[走] link:https://"
"github.com/quarkusio/quarkus/issues/15030[偏] 了。例如，一些云主机供应商只接受 `200` "
"作为健康的定义，所以重定向（一个 `301` "
"）没有达到预期的效果。对于如何关闭非应用端点以恢复以前的行为，也有一些困惑，还有关于如何将特定的端点移出这个非应用端点集合的进一步问题。"

#. type: Plain text
#: _posts/2021-03-04-path-resolution-in-quarkus.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"As an aside, how we got into this situation is not helped by differences in "
"how libraries behave. Vert.x always wants segments beginning with leading "
"slashes when creating routes, for example, while JAX-RS effectively ignores "
"leading slashes in `@Path` annotations. Anyone used to Vert.x always adds "
"leading slashes, and anyone using JAX-RS just does whatever and it magically "
"works."
msgstr ""
"顺便说一句，我们是如何陷入这种情况的，并没有因为库的行为方式不同而得到帮助。例如，在创建路由时，Vert.x 总是希望分段以前面的斜线开始，而 JAX-"
"RS 在 `@Path` 注释中实际上忽略了前面的斜线。任何习惯于Vert.x的人都会添加前导斜杠，而任何使用JAX-"
"RS的人都会做任何事情，并且神奇地工作。"

#. type: Plain text
#: _posts/2021-03-04-path-resolution-in-quarkus.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"In Quarkus, an implementation detail was exposed by accident: non-"
"application endpoints defined by extensions are based on Vert.x routes. "
"Default path configuration values started with slashes to enable quick route "
"creation and allow simple append behavior. There wasn't anything in the "
"early days of Quarkus to suggest this was a bad idea, and developers with "
"experience in JAX-RS didn't have any warnings one way or the other, because "
"JAX-RS handles it."
msgstr ""
"在Quarkus中，一个实施细节被意外地暴露出来：由扩展定义的非应用端点是基于Vert."
"x路由的。默认的路径配置值以斜线开始，以实现快速的路由创建并允许简单的追加行为。在Quarkus的早期，并没有任何东西表明这是一个坏主意，在JAX-"
"RS方面有经验的开发者也没有任何警告，因为JAX-RS会处理它。"

#. type: Plain text
#: _posts/2021-03-04-path-resolution-in-quarkus.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"Now, however, we were in the situation where paths weren't being resolved as "
"people expected, and the configuration changes required to resolve that "
"situation either weren't intuitive or lead to other problems. We ended up "
"putting all of the possible configuration permutations into a spreadsheet so "
"we could see side by side what happened when you combined different "
"configuration values. The results were not awesome. However, the exercise "
"allowed us to step back and look at the big picture to evaluate what needed "
"to change to allow application and non-application endpoints to behave as "
"you need them to."
msgstr ""
"然而，现在我们遇到的情况是，路径没有按照人们的预期得到解决，而解决这种情况所需的配置变化要么不直观，要么会导致其他问题。我们最后把所有可能的配置排列组合放到一个电子表格中，这样我们就可以看到当你结合不同的配置值时，会发生什么。结果不是很好。然而，这个练习让我们退后一步，从大局出发，评估需要改变什么，以使应用和非应用端点的行为符合你的需要。"

#. type: Plain text
#: _posts/2021-03-04-path-resolution-in-quarkus.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"While the set of configuration attributes used to configure paths in Quarkus "
"remains unchanged, how configured values are interpreted is different:"
msgstr "虽然Quarkus中用于配置路径的配置属性集保持不变，但对配置值的解释方式却有所不同。"

#: _posts/2021-03-04-path-resolution-in-quarkus.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"**Endpoint path configuration defaults are now relative values.** `/q` is "
"now `q`, `/metrics` is now `metrics`, etc. This means that, out of the box, "
"these endpoints will resolve relative to the containing root, which is what "
"JAX-RS does per spec, and is what we believe most users intuitively expect."
msgstr ""
"*端点路径配置默认值现在是相对值。* `/q` 现在是 `q` ， `/metrics` 现在是 `metrics` "
"等。这意味着，开箱即用时，这些端点将相对于包含的根进行解析，这正是 JAX-RS 根据规范所做的，也是我们相信大多数用户的直观期望。"

#: _posts/2021-03-04-path-resolution-in-quarkus.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"**Leading slashes in explicitly configured values matter.** We know some of "
"you want to move endpoints to specific places, and the most consistent way "
"to express that intent is to allow you to specify the exact uri you want an "
"endpoint to use. If you specify `/metrics`, that is where you will find the "
"metrics endpoint."
msgstr ""
"*显式配置值中的前导斜线很重要。* 我们知道有些用户希望将端点移动到特定位置，而表达这种意图的最一致方式就是允许用户指定希望端点使用的确切 "
"uri。如果您指定 `/metrics` ，您就可以在这里找到度量端点。"

